        <item>
            <title>【評測】Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 迷你相機，的骰便攜 + 一按即印又得、連落電話再印又得</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-instax-pal-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 12:38:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機測試]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm Instax]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm INSTAX Pal]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[即影即有相機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202492</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>現今社會相信大家人手都會有部智能電話，隨時也可以和朋友「Selfie」留念。數碼相片雖然清晰且容易分享，可是總會讓人感覺缺了點「温度」。Fujifilm 的 instax 系列即影即有相機一直廣受歡迎，即使智能手機攝影普及後仍然非常有人氣。最近 Fujifilm instax 系列又添一員，推出只有乒乓波大小的全新 INSTAX Pal 小型相機，讓攝影變得更輕鬆有趣。今日小編就和 unwire 記者 Weak 妹、Anna 測試 Fujifilm 這部 INSTAX Pal 小型相機，以下會和大家分享一下用後感。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09204.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>5 種顏色選擇，容易襯衫</h2><p>Fujifilm INSTAX 系列在顏色選擇方面一向不會吝嗇，這次 Fujifilm 一口氣推出了乳白、淡粉紅、牛油果綠、薰衣草藍及寶石黑 5 種顏色，而小編收到的就是牛油果綠。清新得來又有點時尚感覺，容易襯衫。質感方面，機身使用防滑的霧麪塑膠質料，讓用家拍照時不容易跣手。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200346 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281-694x462.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN00281.jpg 1280w" alt="" width="694" height="462" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲乳白、淡粉紅、牛油果綠、薰衣草藍及寶石黑</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202894" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09202.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編收到的牛油果綠色 INSTAX Pal</p><h2>外型的骰，輕便易攜</h2><div><p>INSTAX Pal 機身整體尺寸是 42.3 x 44.4 x 43mm (不包括突出部件)，而且僅重 41 g，當作吊飾掛在身上、袋上亦不會覺得重，方便用家隨時帶住 INSTAX Pal 出街，隨時影靚相。</p></div><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09731.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>單手操控非常方便，一按即拍照</h2><p>INSTAX Pal 雖然機仔細細採用掌上的骰設計，但其亦五臟俱全，有多種功能，如果只需拍照，簡單按下後面的快門按鈕即可，此模式下可利用廣角鏡頭進行智能手機難以實現的高位或鋭角拍攝，只要用單手即可輕鬆地高炒或以鋭角進行拍攝。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09755.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲快門設於機背，單手一按就可拍照</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09832.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲超廣角鏡頭非常方便自拍，即使有多幾個朋友也能應付自如</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203453" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09835.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身細細配備廣角鏡，低炒也非常輕鬆</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09828.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>續航力高，充滿電可以影 240 張</h2><p>相機透過 USB Type-C 接口充電，內置鋰離子電池充滿電後可連續拍攝約 240 張。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09199.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身只有拍照按鈕、USB-C 接口及開關掣</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09200.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲底部設有標準尺寸腳架孔及模式轉換鍵</p><h2>多功能圈套配件，可取景、套在手、當腳架</h2><p>相機配有多功能環配件，可套於手上以防止意外掉落，甚至在拍攝合照時可用作簡化的取景器和相機支架。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09748.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可充當簡單取景器</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC09194.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲也可當作輕便腳架</p><h2>拍攝模式 1：「即影即有」  一按即拍馬上印</h2><p>作為即影即有，當然要有「即刻影即刻有」的功能。要啟用「即影即有」功能，首先你身邊要有一部有菲林而且已啟動電源的即影即有打印機，之後你要檢查一下 INSTAX Pal 底部是否已設定為「L」模式（Link 模式）。設定為「L」模式後，即可與 INSTAX Link 系列直接進行藍牙連接，而無需使用專用應用程式。在此模式下，使用 INSTAX Pal 拍攝的照片會立即從 INSTAX Link 打印機自動列印出來，就像使用即影即有相機一樣。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09860.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09861.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要留意是否已設定為「L 模式」</p><p>設定為 L 模式後，按下相機快門鍵，INSTAX Pal 就會自動開始倒計時，計時期間會發出滴滴聲，約 5 秒鐘後，相機就會發出「滴答」水滴聲，示意已經拍攝隨後 INSTAX Pal 會自動連接最近的 INSTAX 打印機列印相片。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09881.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲INSTAX Pal 會自動連接最近的 INSTAX 打印機</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09898.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這樣就可以「即影即有」</p><h2>拍攝模式 2：連接手機 LiveView、遙控拍照後再慢慢印</h2><p>INSTAX Pal 的另一個玩法，是連接到智能電話，利用 INSTAX Pal 拍照後，在電話上執相、加效果再印。用家可下載 Fujifilm 的「INSTAX Pal」應用程式後，以藍牙連接 INSTAX Pal 後就能以電話遙控拍照。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203455" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09836.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載應用程式後就能用電話遠距離控制 INSTAX Pal</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203457" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09876.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203458" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「遠端模式」可以從手機看到 INSTAX Pal 拍攝畫面</p><p>智能電話拍照後，透過藍牙連接 INSTAX Link 系列打印機，即可打印拍到的 instax 菲林相片。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834574_y-1.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在電話上構好圖，按快門鍵</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203460" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834575_y.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Fujifilm 的應用程式會讓你預覽列印出來的樣子<img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203461" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/photo_6219934946617834581_y.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲確認要列印後就可以傳送至 mini LINK 應用程式，連接 INSTAX Link 系列打印機</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09902.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09906.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲接下來就只需要等待相片顯影（大約 90 秒至 2 分鐘）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09907.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲你就可以有一張即影即有</p><p><span lang="EN-US">Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 經已正式</span>發售，備有乳白、淡粉紅、牛油果綠、薰衣草藍及寶石黑，建議零售價為 <span lang="EN-US">$780（寶石黑售價為 $950）。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09831.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203475" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/KAN09886.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/fujifilm-instax-pal-3/dc/">【評測】Fujifilm INSTAX Pal 迷你相機，的骰便攜 + 一按即印又得、連落電話再印又得</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
